---
title: Bacon, Green Bean & Feta Fusilli with Pesto & Lemon
description: The only way to improve the age-old family favourite, pesto pasta, is to add some crispy bacon and creamy feta. With so many textures and well-loved flavours, this dish is anything but ordinary!

*This week the broccolini was not up to our quality standards, so we replaced it with green beans instead! Don't worry, the recipe will still be as delicious!*
